{"tid":1274333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不勇武，不代表無能!]推到 香港民意研究所 啟動 !! (內有捐款方法手把手)","createTime":"2019-07-01T16:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T19:16:59.000Z","uid":272017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93a44a012211d08ea9d026e50b22631e8f676408","tid":1274333,"uid":272017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"民主社會的基石是中立和準確的資訊來源，好讓人民能做出合理的決定，同時令執政者能夠得知正確的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n而 <strong><ins>鍾庭耀教授帶領的&quot;香港大學民意研究計劃&quot;一直為香港提供各種民意研究</ins></strong>。<br />\n(e.g. 官員民望/ 議員表現/ 香港人的身份認同 等爭議性的民意研究)<br />\n鍾庭耀教授的民意研究以其中立性見稱，但同時也被建制中人批評為&quot;過時&quot; 或 &quot;無助管治&quot;。 <br />\n(但無人有能抺黑他們不中立)<br />\n<br />\n好可惜 &quot;香港大學民意研究計劃&quot;今年己是<strong>最後一年由大學資金支援</strong>。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這是繼送中之後又一拆毀民主社會的舉動。</span></strong><br />\n&quot;香港大學民意研究計劃&quot;今後改名為&quot;香港民意研究所&quot;要靠自己集資自生自滅。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鍾庭耀教授的團隊要600萬啟動資金去進行獨立的第一步。</span></strong> (買器材、租地方、人工.....)<br />\n<br />\n從我觀察&quot;香港民意研究所&quot;網站 ( <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNoh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=759a1cc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk</a> ) 的結構，其介面設計真的十分差。 <br />\n(很典型的學者制作，只精專自己的範疇)<br />\n令人有心都不知如何捐款。<br />\n<br />\n我們當中或許沒有勇武的本錢(年老、有家庭負擔)，但還有能做的事。<br />\n我就先行一步，先捐$1000，再把相關的步驟寫下給大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>事前準備:</ins><br />\n1. PAYPAL 這個 <strong>真。外國勢力</strong>電子錢包的 賬戶 一個。<br />\n2. 手機，因為VISA/MASTER CARD 會在進行大額交易時用上手機驗証碼<br />\n<br />\n<ins>捐款方法手把手</ins><br />\n1. 先訪問捐款頁面。按下&quot;Donation 捐款 / subscription 贊助&quot;按鈕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNoh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=6597ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n&lt;001&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10YAj2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10YAj2a.png&h=75d48e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 填上EMAIL，之後按CONTINUE<br />\n&lt;002&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0st1fAF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0st1fAF.png&h=b0816e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 選要捐助的金額<br />\n&lt;003&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7K6Kdns.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7K6Kdns.png&h=dc7319ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. &quot;PAYMENT ADDRESS&quot; 這個位置困住最多人。 其實只要你有一個已經SET-UP 完的PAYPAL ID，PAYMENT ADDRESS 不用填。 直接按&quot;Pay With Paypal&quot;<br />\n&lt;004&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dsYhPd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dsYhPd.jpg&h=84c65bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 之後會有個POP-UP 彈出來，用PAYPAL ID 登入。<br />\n&lt;005&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3H5Hf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3H5Hf1.png&h=1ecf16aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. LOGIN 完係咁樣，確定資料沒錯就按&quot;CONTINUE&quot;<br />\n&lt;006&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22i8E2X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22i8E2X.png&h=dc7b54b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. &quot;PAYMENT ADDRESS &quot;已經幫你填好了。 但不要停，按下最後&quot;DONATE&quot;才算成事。<br />\n&lt;008&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mq2UABq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMq2UABq.png&h=a91f9181&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8. 最後會有一封E-MAIL 寄到你在第一步提供的EMAIL ADDRESS 中<br />\n&lt;009&gt;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nogx6Jz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnogx6Jz.png&h=4d0ca98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6YMrJA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6YMrJA.png&h=e6db90d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考報導:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21727/鍾庭耀-香港民研-特首民望-21730/鍾庭耀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21727%2F%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B-21730%2F%E9%8D%BE%E5%BA%AD%E8%80%80&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNoh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=7b05558e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21727/鍾庭耀-香港民研-特首民望-21730/鍾庭耀</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>後記:</ins><br />\n心中很爭扎應否在大家都看著立法會的一班年輕人的時候發這篇文。<br />\n但最終還是發了。 <br />\n不知能否傳逹，但我想說的是&quot;不勇武也有很多事可做&quot;。<br />\n我老是期望年輕人可以用他們的勇武落區保護文宣的街站。但永遠事與願違。"},{"pid":"623f8f87da2833d48ddeb15d314570404b4bfee4","tid":1274333,"uid":213893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf6063d3ebdc1971352bbd1cf48c012ddb73986","tid":1274333,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e41adfa8467ac617f9ab497434e1d8460e28de9f","tid":1274333,"uid":269572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"366481cb57a3a37b2dbb235090923e8b52590211","tid":1274333,"uid":272978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"而家用apple pay用信用卡都捐到錢。同課金一樣咁邊方便。推。"},{"pid":"19fc4c358d934572ebe039813197023729927fed","tid":1274333,"uid":180429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}